high_descs: Turn right and go to the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife to the left of the tomato.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Cut the tomato on the second shelf of the fridge.
Move left and go to the fridge.
Put the knife on the second shelf of the fridge.
Move right and go to the fridge.
Pick up a slice of tomato in the fridge.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Cook the slice of tomato in the microwave and pick it back up.
Turn around and go to the green trash can in the corner.
Put the slice of tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in the trash can.

high_descs: turn to the right and move to the counter with the dishwasher below
pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle
turn to the right and move to the fridge on the left, turn to face the fridge
open the door of the fridge, cut the tomato in the back right corner of the second shelf with the knife and close the door
stay in front of the refrigerator for a few seconds
open the door to the fridge again and put the knife on the second shelf and close the door
stay in front of the refrigerator for a few seconds
open the door and pick up one slice of the tomato that was sliced and close the door
move to the left of the fridge to face the microwave
open the microwave door, put the slice of tomato in to it, close the door, cook for 3 seconds, open the door, remove the tomato slice and close the door.
turn to the right, moving passed the fridge and at the wall turn right and move to the trash can ahead
put the slice of tomato in to the trash can
anns.task_desc: heat a chilled slice of tomato followed by putting it in the trash can

high_descs: Turn right, go to the counter
Pick up the knife from the counter
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the fridge
Slice the tomato in the fridge
Move a bit  to the left
Put the knife in the fridge
Move a bit to the right
Pick up a tomato slice from the fridge
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the microwave
Turn right, go forward, turn right, go to the bin
Put the tomato slice in the bin
anns.task_desc: Cook a slice of tomato and put it in the bin
